Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.583
(gentle music)

00:00:10.750 --> 00:00:14.710
- So we get questions
from both men and women

00:00:14.710 --> 00:00:19.710
about bulking or getting
big with using X3.

00:00:20.640 --> 00:00:22.940
So I'm gonna answer both questions.

00:00:22.940 --> 00:00:24.200
Like what happens to men

00:00:24.200 --> 00:00:27.470
and what happens to
women when they use X3?

00:00:27.470 --> 00:00:28.870
I'll start with women.

00:00:28.870 --> 00:00:32.150
They read that I put
on 45 pounds of muscle

00:00:32.150 --> 00:00:35.460
in the first two years and
lost 16 pounds of body fat.

00:00:35.460 --> 00:00:37.130
They like the fat loss part,

00:00:37.130 --> 00:00:40.140
they really don't wanna
put on 45 pounds of muscle.

00:00:40.140 --> 00:00:43.870
Well, for those women who are concerned

00:00:43.870 --> 00:00:46.147
about too much muscle mass,

00:00:46.147 --> 00:00:49.810
you don't really have the biochemistry

00:00:49.810 --> 00:00:52.570
to put on that kind of mass as a female.

00:00:52.570 --> 00:00:55.720
So what ends up happening
with women who use this,

00:00:55.720 --> 00:00:58.210
and you can see in some of
the before and after pictures

00:00:58.210 --> 00:01:02.170
on the website, the women
end up looking more feminine

00:01:02.170 --> 00:01:06.160
because the muscles do
get a little bigger,

00:01:06.160 --> 00:01:08.050
but they also get harder

00:01:08.050 --> 00:01:11.020
and then the body fat
surrounding them is dropped.

00:01:11.020 --> 00:01:13.080
So they just look more defined,

00:01:13.080 --> 00:01:15.460
maybe a little more athletic
or a lot more athletic,

00:01:15.460 --> 00:01:17.460
depending on their nutrition.

00:01:17.460 --> 00:01:22.460
But ultimately, nobody's
putting on too much size

00:01:23.590 --> 00:01:27.610
so that they're really tipping the scale

00:01:27.610 --> 00:01:29.270
when it comes to muscularity.

00:01:29.270 --> 00:01:31.210
So moving on to men.

00:01:31.210 --> 00:01:33.520
Men respond in a very different way

00:01:33.520 --> 00:01:36.040
because they have the
hormones and biochemistry

00:01:36.040 --> 00:01:38.360
to add a lot more muscle mass.

00:01:38.360 --> 00:01:40.290
There are people who put
on 20 pounds of muscles

00:01:40.290 --> 00:01:41.240
in six months.

00:01:41.240 --> 00:01:44.940
Quite a few of them, you
can see them on the website

00:01:44.940 --> 00:01:46.800
in the before and after section.

00:01:46.800 --> 00:01:48.730
Men and women respond differently,

00:01:48.730 --> 00:01:52.440
but both end up looking very athletic

00:01:52.440 --> 00:01:54.083
with their respected genders.

